headline: Has General Dynamics Run Too Far After 29% Rally Or Is Value Still Left?
summary: If you have been wondering whether General Dynamics is still worth buying after its big run, you are not alone. This is exactly the kind of stock where valuation really matters. Even after a slight pullback of 1.7% over the past week and 1.6% over the last month, the stock is still up 28.9% year to date and 30.9% over the last year, compounding to 154.0% over five years.
